fields.name: alert
fields.description: generate an alert using the selected alert method, and then log the packet

fields.name: reject
fields.description: block the packet, log it, and then send a TCP reset if the protocol is TCP or an ICMP port unreacha

fields.name: sdrop
fields.description: block the packet but do not log it.

fields.name: activate
fields.description: alert and then turn on another dynamic rule

fields.name: dynamic
fields.description: remain idle until activated by an activate rule, then act as a log rule
